<h2 class="bold font-l">Zenitsu</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
There isn't a day that goes by where Zenitsu Agatsuma doesn't try to hit on any girl he sees. Not even Nezuko, a demon, is safe. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CasanovaWannabe" class='trope-example-link'>Casanova Wannabe</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
